OL,3,CBBC boss says broadcaster has asked
OL,4,CHuw Edwards to return #200,000 salary
OL,6,FBBC Director-General Tim Davie says
OL,7,Fthe broadcaster has asked Huw Edwards
OL,8,Fto return his #200,000 salary after he
OL,9,Fwas given a six month suspended prison
OL,10,Fsentence on Monday for accessing
OL,11,Findecent images of children.
OL,13,FSpeaking at the Royal Television
OL,14,FSociety (RTS) London conference, Mr
OL,15,FDavie said Edwards' crimes were
OL,16,F"appalling" and that the BBC's
OL,17,Freputation was impacted.
