OL,3,CBBC boss says broadcaster has asked
OL,4,CHuw Edwards to return #200,000 salary
OL,6,F"There's no doubt that an affair like
OL,7,Fthis impacts our reputation, and I
OL,8,Fdon't know yet in terms of just the
OL,9,Fdirect impact on trust," he added.
OL,11,FWhen asked how the BBC was getting
OL,12,Fback Edwards' #200,000 salary, he
OL,13,Freplied: "We want the money back and
OL,14,Fwe've asked for it back, and we're
OL,15,Fwaiting to hear back."
OL,17,FMr Davie was also asked why Edwards'
OL,18,Fpay continued after the BBC was made
OL,19,Faware of charges against the 63-year-
OL,20,Fold.
