OL,6,FHe replied that "we decided that pay
OL,7,Fcontinues until someone is charged"
OL,8,Fand added: "I think it was the right
OL,9,Fdecision based on current policy."
OL,11,FWhen asked Edwards would ever work for
OL,12,Fthe BBC again, Davie replied: "For
OL,13,Fobvious reasons, this man has has just
OL,14,Fbeen convicted of appalling crimes,
OL,15,Fand it's pretty straightforward in my
OL,16,Fmind that I can't see him working at
OL,17,Fthe BBC."
